{
  "id": "ex_technical_04d4bd3e",
  "intent": "Execute NEBNext Ultra II Directional RNA Library Prep Kit Part 2 protocol for RNA isolation using magnetic bead purification. Add 50\u00b5L magnetic beads to samples, perform thermocycler incubation, engage magnetic module at 8mm height, remove supernatant with P300 and P20 multi-channel pipettes. Wash beads twice with 170\u00b5L buffer, add 50\u00b5L Tris buffer with thermocycler step, add 50\u00b5L binding buffer with 5-minute incubation and magnetic separation. Perform final wash with 180\u00b5L buffer, elute with 11.5\u00b5L strand primer mix after thermocycler treatment, and transfer 10\u00b5L purified RNA to final plate using magnetic separation.",
